ina/SU.","guid":"2qpHgetWqgJC5HNecSW8Xg","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"66","text":"• Contraindicaciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"75","parent":"74","text":"• Insuficiencia renal grave (TFG < 45 ml/min/1.73m²).","guid":"Krgyg9QOYubimZZBiHVfrQ","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"74","text":"• Cetoacidosis diabética.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"74","text":"• Ingesta excesiva alcohol","guid":"KvGXegPl1hvJdn9MJbqxMA","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"74","text":"• Enfermedad aguda intercurrente","guid":"3wlyNjNAOv4cEY8d_rJsyQ","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"74","text":"• Embarazo","guid":"VIfxKEaTp0yOtTd-75i-PQ","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"74","text":"• Trastornos conducta alimentaria","guid":"ZGzIFazAZw1c3LVSp2p-gQ","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"74","text":"• Suspender 48-72 h previo a cirugía (111,112).","guid":"K5RZR406td22z-dW1A3u7g","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"66","text":"• Consideraciones:","guid":"","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"• Control función renal ⟶ 3 meses.","guid":"0LHP-BZa0Uz_ubhv59N2wg","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"• Hidratación adecuada.","guid":"","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"82","text":"• Precaución en:","guid":"s76YHyvWha6v8xpqzyX0AQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"• Adultos mayores","guid":"Y8TWkcm3y-UqUBXgb6Lchw","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"85","text":"• Fragilidad/deterioro cognitivo","guid":"ARs3152jLZXa6-j1tYe-PA","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"85","text":"• Depleción volumen/uso diuréticos","guid":"kdOQ-Oi0Cj-FFYxDCnDAyQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"85","text":"• Infecciones urinarias recurrentes","guid":"LszfRBNdYeHQTvr9_cJ7gg","children":[]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"• Descompensación aguda diabetes (>200 mg/dL, A1c >9%)","guid":"6CC97L3j5g_eKprTDlElDg","children":[]},{"id":"91","parent":"85","text":"• IMC <25 kg/m²","guid":"1Ix59DPpi86g0LAmqPqDcg","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"85","text":"• Úlc